What does the Eye command?

764
01:09:25,340 --> 01:09:27,140
We have work to do.

765
01:10:10,040 --> 01:10:14,440
The trees are strong, my lord.
Their roots go deep.

766
01:10:15,040 --> 01:10:16,840
Rip them all down.

767
