817
01:20:21,040 --> 01:20:22,440
Arwen...

818
01:20:22,440 --> 01:20:25,640
...ride hard. Don't Look back.

819
01:20:30,840 --> 01:20:35,040
What are you doing?!
Those wraiths are still out there!

820
