The same blood flows in my veins.

949
01:35:30,840 --> 01:35:33,340
The same weakness.

950
01:35:36,140 --> 01:35:38,840
Your time will come.

951
01:35:39,140 --> 01:35:43,340
You will face the same evil.
And you will defeat it.

